Somizi dumps Idols for United states The idols' recent judge has been rumoured to have left South Africa to go start a new show. Apparently Khanyi Mbau on her show the scoop on Wednesday said that Somizi has travelled to United states to work with Jennifer Lopez Somizi's close friend has confirmed that Somizi is indeed out of the county working on a bigger show. Somizi's fans are devastated and angry about him dumping them just to live in greener pastures. One fan twitted "ses buti could have warned us not just make us love him then leave us "